  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下GUI工具层的类关系。目前guitool这个命名空间下面有个TabTemplate，它是所有标签页配置的抽象模板。然后具体的设置项应该放在TabSettings里，这个类需要继承TabTemplate。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSettings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，TabSettings作为TabTemplate的子类。那TabSettings和Model之间的关系呢？我注意到Model是在hexgui命名空间下的，它们之间应该有数据关联吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabSettings",
        "Model",
        "hexgui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，TabSettings会包含一个Model实例，是组合关系。因为TabSettings的生命周期管理着Model，设置面板销毁的时候，对应的模型数据也要一起释放。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabSettings",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "组合关系，用实心菱形表示。那我再确认一下命名空间的划分：TabTemplate和TabSettings都放在guitool下，Model单独放在hexgui下，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "hexgui",
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSettings",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这样分层比较清晰。guitool专注于界面工具组件，hexgui放核心数据模型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "hexgui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画好了：guitool命名空间包含TabTemplate，TabSettings继承自TabTemplate；然后TabSettings通过组合关联持有hexgui命名空间下的Model。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSettings",
        "Model",
        "guitool",
        "hexgui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了——TabTemplate和TabSettings的继承方向要反过来确认一下。是TabSettings继承TabTemplate，不是TabTemplate继承TabSettings，你画的方向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSettings"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "放心，箭头是从TabSettings指向TabTemplate的，子类指向父类，方向正确。组合关系也是TabSettings包含Model，没有画反。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabSettings",
        "TabTemplate",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
